, 
<figureCitation id="13112A3EFFB8DF28B2FE7822FE78FC7B" box="[399,426,886,912]" captionStart="Figure 42–46" captionStartId="21.[192,268,1679,1705]" captionTargetBox="[192,1440,213,1650]" captionTargetId="figure-12@21.[192,1440,213,1653]" captionTargetPageId="21" captionText="Figure 42–46. Female genitalia of Eucosmocydia. 42) E. lecaniodiscana, USNM slide 142,063. 43) E. pancoviana, USNM slide 153682. 44) E. kirimiriana, USNM slide 143,280. 45) E. macabensis, USNM slide 153,710. 46) E. hymenosa, USNM slide 143,024." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6533448" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6533448/files/figure.png" pageId="20" pageNumber="19">44</figureCitation>
